snippet: The British Olympic Association ratified the nomination of Lutalo Muhammad to its tae kwon do team Friday, excluding Aaron Cook, who is ranked No. 1 in his weight class.
abstract: The British Olympic Association ratified the nomination of Lutalo Muhammad to its tae kwon do team Friday, excluding Aaron Cook, who is ranked No. 1 in his weight class.

headline.main: Britain Confirms Tae Kwon Do Choice Is Not No. 1 Fighter
